# Button Demo - multiple button variants and styles
Source demos/settings.tape
Output demos/gifs/button.gif

Hide
Type "cargo run --example button_demo"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show

Sleep 800ms

# Cycle through buttons
Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Tab
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Sleep 1s

Type "q"
